HOW TO PACKAGE AND DEPLOY A NEW VERSION OF XTREEMFS
===================================================

1. create a new release branch/tag for the new version in the SVN
2. check out the release branch/tag
3. cd <checkout>/packaging
4. ./build_release-pacakges <release-version> ..
5. ./deploy_release-packages dist test

If the test distribution works w/o any problems:
6. ./deploy_release-packages dist release
